---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms & Conditions - MSZ Software House">
  <main class="bg-white dark:bg-charcoal-900">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white tracking-tighter">Terms & Conditions</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-charcoal-800/80 dark:text-gray-300">
          Last updated: December 2025
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none dark:prose-invert">
        <div class="space-y-8">
          
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
            <p class="text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300">
              By using the MSZ website, digital products, templates, tools, or services, you agree to follow these Terms & Conditions. If you do not agree, please stop using our services.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-4">2. What We Provide (Service Description)</h2>
            <p class="text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              MSZ now operates under a fair, legal, 100% ethical model.
            </p>
            
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Premium Digital Products</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li>Canva templates</li>
              <li>Notion systems</li>
              <li>Courses & eBooks</li>
              <li>Reels/Preset Packs</li>
              <li>Social Media Toolkits</li>
              <li>Website Templates</li>
              <li>Automation Workflows (n8n / Make)</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Digital Services</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li>Website Development</li>
              <li>Social Media Management</li>
              <li>Branding & Content Creation</li>
              <li>Marketing Funnels</li>
              <li>SaaS Setup & AI Automation Services</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Verified Legal SaaS Subscriptions</h3>
            <p class="text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              We ONLY provide tools that are sourced:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li>legally</li>
              <li>ethically</li>
              <li>without carding</li>
              <li>without tricks</li>
              <li>without violating provider rules</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300">
              No illegal, cracked, or manipulated accounts are sold.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-4">3. Nature of Digital Products</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300">
              <li>All digital products are non-tangible assets delivered electronically. You receive access via download links, files, or cloud dashboards.</li>
              <li>Digital products are non-refundable once downloaded or accessed.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-4">4. Payment Terms</h2>
            <p class="text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              Payment must be completed before order processing. We accept:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li>Bank Transfer</li>
              <li>Easypaisa</li>
              <li>JazzCash</li>
              <li>Nayapay</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300">
              To ensure fairness and proof, customers must provide a payment receipt on WhatsApp.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-4">5. Delivery Policy</h2>
            
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Digital Products</h3>
            <p class="text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              Instant or within 1 hour (auto delivery or cloud link)
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Services</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li>Delivery timeline will be shared individually</li>
              <li>Project-based services include milestones</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Verified SaaS Tools (Legal Only)</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300">
              <li>Delivered within 2–12 hours</li>
              <li>No carding, no VPN tricks, no illegal sourcing</li>
              <li>Only official & legitimate access</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-4">6. Usage Rules</h2>
            <p class="text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              To maintain fairness for all customers, users agree to:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li>Not resell digital products without resell license</li>
              <li>Not claim authorship for MSZ templates</li>
              <li>Not misuse or redistribute paid content</li>
              <li>Not engage in illegal, unethical, or fraudulent use of SaaS tools</li>
              <li>Not shift emails/passwords on SaaS accounts without approval (if part of service)</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300">
              Misuse may result in termination without refund.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-4">7. Warranty & Support Policy</h2>
            
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Digital Products</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li>Lifetime access (unless stated)</li>
              <li>Free fixes for file corruption or incorrect links</li>
              <li>No refunds after download</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Services</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li>Limited support as per service agreement</li>
              <li>Revisions depend on purchased package</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-3">SaaS Tools (Legal Access Only)</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300">
              <li>Warranty depends on provider policies</li>
              <li>We ensure delivery of working access</li>
              <li>If the provider changes policy, MSZ is not responsible</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-4">8. Refund Policy</h2>
            <p class="text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              Refunds are allowed only under these conditions:
            </p>
            
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Eligible Refunds</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li>You purchased the WRONG product by mistake and have NOT downloaded it</li>
              <li>File/link is corrupted and cannot be replaced</li>
              <li>Service was not delivered, and project didn't start</li>
              <li>SaaS access was not delivered</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Not Eligible</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li>Digital products already downloaded</li>
              <li>Templates already accessed</li>
              <li>You "changed your mind"</li>
              <li>You used the SaaS access successfully</li>
              <li>Mishandling from user side</li>
              <li>Attempt to misuse refund after usage</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300">
              Refunds are reviewed within 24–48 hours.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-4">9. Legal & Ethical Compliance</h2>
            <p class="text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              MSZ strictly follows:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li>Fair business practices</li>
              <li>Halal earning principles</li>
              <li>No illegal tools</li>
              <li>No carding</li>
              <li>No hacked / cracked tools</li>
              <li>No country manipulation tricks</li>
              <li>No fraudulent accounts</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300">
              We only sell: Verified, legal, fair-source products & subscriptions.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-4">10. Limitation of Liability</h2>
            <p class="text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              We are not responsible for:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li>Policy changes from third-party software companies</li>
              <li>User mistakes or misuse</li>
              <li>Account bans caused by customer violations</li>
              <li>Delays caused by service providers</li>
              <li>Loss of data due to user actions</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300">
              Our responsibility is limited to providing the purchased product/service correctly.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-4">11. Modification of Terms</h2>
            <p class="text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300">
              We may update these Terms anytime. Continued use = You accept new terms.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-4">12. Contact & Support</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300">
              <li>WhatsApp: +92 333 2040826</li>
              <li>Email: mszsoftwarehouse@gmail.com</li>
              <li>Website: mszsoftwarehouse.com</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-4">13. Copyright Notice</h2>
            <p class="text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300">
              All content, designs, templates, and products are the property of MSZ. Unauthorised resale, distribution, or replication is strictly prohibited.
            </p>
          </section>

          <div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-cream-100 dark:bg-charcoal-800 rounded-lg border border-cream-400 dark:border-charcoal-700">
            <p class="text-sm text-charcoal-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-center">
              Last updated: December 2025<br>
              © 2025 MSZ Software House. All rights reserved.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>